the lazarus edge
a throwing dagger obtained on the crimson isle that can be dungeonised with a 1 time payment of 500 wither essence and starred with crimson essence
when thrown it will bounce between 15 enemies healing the user each time it hits a mob in a simillar manner to a souped up FOT.

whenever you star any item no matter what it becomes soulbound

you should be able to click on plasmafluxes or sos flares to choose which to use if there is two within a certain range

a deployable that just gives a bunch of raw damage like crit damage strength and base dmg, or a dmg multiplyer.
